_sText:
This is a optimized version of gg_office. I have increased the FPS by about 30 FPS, i think. Try it your self. ;)

What I have done with the map: I added nodraw to between 300-500 faces. And i re-sized some floor that was not needed as big as it was.

Info from old map:
Gungam map based on the official cs_office map. Maximum 40 people, 20 spawns every team. 3734 faces average fps around 40, but i've got a slow computer, my friends got an fps around 60-70 Grtz ievel pm for any information about the map
